reviews.text: Food is really good, service is average.  But always get bothered by them serving "boiling hot" water on glass cups for children age 5 to 6, it is obviously very dangerous to touch and children cannot drink it immediately even they are thirsty while eating food. Impression is very poor. Not certain why serving chilled water or room temperature water seemed pretty challenging for the waiters in this restaurant.  Compared to restaurants in Japan, nearly all restaurants are able to provide free chilled water.
Good quality of food with reasonable price
Nice cozy atmosphere with great attentive staff. Food is fresh and authentic izakaya styled food.
A nice range of Japanese food ranging from sushi, skewers and tempura, but a tad pricey
Food quality is okay but not great, price is a little expensive.  Sashimi is fresh, grilled fish neck taste good.  Grilled ox tongue and cold noodles are just so-so.

reviews.text: The mall is spacious and clean. It is very comfortable to walk around. People can have lunch or dinner in the mall as a lot of restaurants and fast food shops are available there.
A popular mall at Olympic station for local . Many mid- level shops in Phase 1 to  phase 3 Plaza. Easy to spend a few hours here.
Decent shopping variety.  More to local families. And has 3 different buildings.
A modern shopping mall with a fantastic food court. Close to the MTR,  bus and taxi stands.

A large shopping mall with a few phases joined together. The direction is not too clear hence makes it harder to find shops if you are new to the place. Overall the mall is clean and comfortable to shop. Linked with the mtr station so getting there is easy.
